text: Éva Molnár (born 25 May 1958) is a Hungarian rower. She competed in the women's coxless pair event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== == External links == * * * * Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Hungary Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Budapest
